      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "for(;nt i  = 0 ; i < n-1; i++){\n       for(int j = i ; j < n ; j++){\n                sum=0\n                for(int r = i  ; r<=j ;r++){\n                    sum+=arr[r]\n                }\n \n        }\n}",
